CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: In Figma, designers work alongside developers, product managers, researchers, marketers, writers, and other non-designers who. Together, these teams share and explore ideas, align on a vision, visualize concepts, and translate them into coded products - all on a single, connected, AI-powered platform that collaborators around the world can access with a URL. While Figma began as a browser-based tool for designing user interfaces, our platform has expanded to help teams go from idea to product all in one place.
